                        and all necessary amenities. Two cozy bedrooms, each furnished with king-size beds, offer restful retreats. 
                        A separate bathroom with a generous walk-in shower adds to the comfort. The main terrace boasts a 
                        traditional Greek wood oven, perfect for hosting barbecue evenings.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Ascending to the first floor reveals a charming loft accommodating two to four occupants. 
                        Here, a sleeping area with a plush king-size bed awaits, alongside a cozy sitting area with a 
                        convertible sofa bed. The accompanying bathroom offers a lavish bathtub. 
                        The terrace provides panoramic vistas of the azure Aegean Sea and the majestic Fengari Mountain.
                    <p>
