                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The expansive garden, adorned with fruit and olive trees, hosts a private swimming pool for 
                        refreshing dips on warm days. This idyllic setting is unparalleled in Samothrace, with both 
                        garden and pool maintenance ensured throughout your stay.
